data.description: It doesn't get any better than this!!!! Newly renovated rare DUPLEX located in the HOT Vine City neighborhood. Literally walking distance to the mercedes benz stadium, beltline trail and eateries, Westside Park, and all the new hot spots of Atlanta. Minutes from downtown Atlanta, GA Aquarium, Georgia Tech, Atlanta University Center,Echo West and home of Microsoft! West Midtown. Duplex features 2 spacious units complete with 2 bedroom/ 1 bathroom each. Brand new paint, kitchen, flooring, new roof, new plumbing and new electrical. This is prime real estate in Atlanta. A property that can easily be a money maker with rent in the area going above two thousand for a 2 bedroom. A TRUE GEM! You don't want to miss out on this investment.
